MAIN_MESSAGE: There is a power cut affecting the CW6 postcode areas of Eaton and Rushton. Repairs are taking longer than expected because of further materials required on site to repair a fault on the overhead line network and our team are now working to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 5:30PM. We will update this message if this information changes. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 3:16PM on 14th November 2020.
